body:
I suggest we make the following change instead. Either both `custom_grouping_object` and `CustomGroupingObjectType` appear or neither exists.

``` protobuf
message CustomGroupingObject {
    required byte custom_grouping_object = 1;
    required CustomGroupingObjectType type = 2;
}
...
{
   ...
   optional CustomGroupingObject obj = 5;
}
```

However, if this change breaks backward compatibility a lot, your change is fine.
